{"word":"G5320 - φανερῶς - phanerōs - fan-er-oce' - Evidently","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φανερῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phanerōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fan-er-oce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Evidently</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வெளியரங்கமாய், பிரத்தியட்சமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. plainly, clearly, manifestly"},{"paragraph":"2. openly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G5318 - φανερός - phanerós - fan-er-os'/5318\">G5318</a>; <i>plainly</i>, that is, <i>clearly</i> or <i>publicly:</i> - evidently, openly.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1718/1718\">G1718</a>, <a href=\"#/G2014/2014\">G2014</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015/2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016/2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316/5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318/5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319/5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320/5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321/5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322/5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324/5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325/5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326/5326\">G5326</a>"}]}